STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Andrew T. PENDER, a/k/a Drew Pender, Defendant-Petitioner. C-300 September Term 2018
081176 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 2, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003095-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
